            <h5><a href="/card/LL07-059/">LL07-059 "G Senjou no Cinderella"</a></h5>
            <div class="question" id="059">
                If there are multiple pieces of this song in the live, will the target live P be added for each piece?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                yes. It will be +1 for each song of this live.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="059">
                When the target live P was 9 points, this song was "live" and the live P became 9 points. Will this be a winner?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                No. Since the target live P was +1, we need 1 more point.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="059">
                In a situation where there are 3 or more people playing and there is a player who has already won with 9 points, what will happen if this song is played "live"?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Players who have already won will remain victorious. The target live P of the remaining players is +1.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="059">
                The player who played this song "live" won. [During Live] Will the skill continue after that?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                yes. The [During Live] skill continues until the end of this game.
            </div>

